{"tid":1366561,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線]親政府極權分子要求立即拘捕林卓延朱凱迪獲大量支持","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:02:20.000Z","uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"84d77857e2d0bf6f5c26cd4994ccf59e0ca48abc","tid":1366561,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28395658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D28395658&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=4e7e23c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28395658</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZsT9jq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZsT9jq.jpg&h=19bf8698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8-095800881.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8-095800881.html&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=77292476\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8-095800881.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】「保衛香港運動」今午由西鐵元朗站附近的公園，遊行到元朗警署報案，指立法會議員林卓廷、朱凱迪等人，是星期日元朗暴力襲撃事件的罪魁禍首，要求警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n成員在元朗警署門外高叫「還我法治」、「林卓廷最無恥」、「黑衣口罩暴民」，拉起「支持警察嚴正執法 嚴懲暴徒還我法治」的橫幅。他們向元朗警區指揮區李偉文發信，要求拘捕林卓廷及黑衣人，涉嫌非法集結；又要求警方拒絕批出周六元朗遊行的不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n警方今午約4時已向周六元朗遊行發出反對通知書，遊行申請人鍾健平表明上訴。"},{"pid":"b660290eadaabe88f5f4b41d2b6a2f9c89514644","tid":1366561,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"睇埋班親政府極權分子d留言同投票，原來咁多人可以指鹿為馬"},{"pid":"94b59b4876c26c4bb0e517bc3ad69e2ea590ea92","tid":1366561,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7dc09c3cdb68d13e18b9edbb379af00d9fea9b","tid":1366561,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b660290eadaabe88f5f4b41d2b6a2f9c89514644","tid":1366561,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"睇埋班親政府極權分子d留言同投票，原來咁多人可以指鹿為馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"都係網絡水軍   叫佢出黎咪又係無錢唔撚出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下就算     唔順氣咪送啲文宣 長輩圖反擊"},{"pid":"d03a6e31230ff6abe49572781c0926db79ea5455","tid":1366561,"uid":94515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"843慢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ae69ab289f4fabe098fc4d4c8491e1088df60d","tid":1366561,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"同白衣人搭哂膊頭，比like讚英雄嘅係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣調轉嚟講都得"},{"pid":"b7bdcd6b2a4bdf6d10de9705e7e84a454b0879a0","tid":1366561,"uid":76844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"犬儒"},{"pid":"bb901690a058db508a78ecba0b4e56b7d2e2a933","tid":1366561,"uid":288869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"今期自從